-- Vedanta's Plan to Buy Cairn India Assets May be Delayed, Express Reports
-- B y   U n n i   K r i s h n a n
-- 2010-10-01T01:36:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-01/vedanta-s-plan-to-buy-cairn-india-assets-may-be-delayed-express-reports.html
The Indian government’s decision on
whether to approve Vedanta Resources Plc’s purchase of Cairn
Energy Plc’s local unit may be delayed as the petroleum ministry
is expected to seek more information from all parties involved,
the Financial Express said, without saying where it got the
information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
